Requires:

    * Python 2.6
    * Latest Setuptools
    * sqlite3
    * libsqlite3-dev

How to install (as root or with sudo):

#> sudo python setup.py install

Database will be created for you (sqlite by default in '/etc/sire/db.sqlite').
Config file will be copied to '/etc/sire/sire.conf'.

Read '/etc/sire/sire.conf' for instructions on how to configure.
